Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, my name is Sebastian Harris, how may I assist you today?
Hi Sebastian, this is John Smith. I just wanted to call and let you know how happy I am with the service I received from your agency on my recent trip from New York to Los Angeles.
That's great to hear, John! Thank you for choosing our agency. Can you tell me more about what specifically made you happy with the service?
Sure! The flight was on time, the hotel accommodations were exactly what I needed, and the staff at the hotel were very friendly and helpful.
I appreciate the feedback, John. As a thank you for your kind words, I'd like to offer you a 10% discount on your next booking with us. Is there anything else I can help you with?
Actually, I do need some tech support. I'm having trouble accessing my itinerary for an upcoming trip from Dallas to Miami.
I apologize for the inconvenience, John. Can you please provide me with your reservation number and I can help you access your itinerary?
Yes, it's XYZ123 and the flight is on June 18th at 2 pm.
Thank you, John. Let me take a look. It looks like you are all set for your flight from Dallas to Miami. Your itinerary is available on our website, let's walk through getting there together.
Okay, I'm logged onto the website. What do I do next?
In the top right corner, you'll see a button that says 'My Trips', click on that and it will take you to a page where you can enter your reservation number and last name to access your itinerary.
Okay, I found it! Thank you so much for your help, Sebastian. You've been very patient and helpful in resolving my issue.
You're welcome, John. I'm glad I could help. Is there anything else you need assistance with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you again!
You're welcome, John. Have a great day!
